Police have urged the public to help them locate the teenager. It is unknown whether she left with friends, said police spokesperson Hein Hendricks. Sumaya is light of complexion and at the time of her disappearance she was wearing grey tights, a red jacket and pink slippers. Anyone with information is requested to Contact Bishop Lavis SAPS at 021 935 9802 or Warrant Officer Joseph Swartbooi at 082 302 8437. Information can also be anonymously shared via Crime Stop on 086 001 0111 or SMS Crime Line on 32211. 